  "text": "Insulin was extracted from plasma with a solid-phase extraction procedure by Visser et al. [CITATION_1] . This method can also extract insulin in a single extraction procedure. The mean recovery is better for plasma than those of the studies reported by Ravi et al. [CITATION_2] and Visser et al. [CITATION_3] .",
